ent\"><code>AnimationPlaybackEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationTimeline\"><code>AnimationTimeline</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/getAnimations\"><code>Document.getAnimations()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/timeline\"><code>Document.timeline</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DocumentTimeline\"><code>DocumentTimeline</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Element/animate\"><code>Element.animate()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/KeyframeEffect\"><code>KeyframeEffect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>Esta es una <a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Guidelines/Conventions_definitions#experimental\">tecnología experimental</a></strong><br>Comprueba la <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">Tabla de compabilidad de navegadores</a> cuidadosamente antes de usarla en producción.</p></div><p></p>\n\n<p>La propiedad <code><strong>Animation</strong></code><strong><code>.id</code></strong> de la <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Animations_API\">Web Animations API</a> devuelve o establece una cadena(string) utilizado para identificar la animación.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sintaxis","title":"Sintaxis","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">var <em>animationsId</em> = <em>Animation</em>.id;\n\n<em>Animation</em>.id = <em>newIdString</em>;\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"valor","title":"Valor","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Un <a href=\"/es/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>DOMString</code></a> que se puede usar para identificar la animación, o <code>null</code> si la animación no tiene <code>id</code>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ejemplos","title":"Ejemplos","isH3":false,"content":"<p>En el ejemplo <a href=\"https://codepen.io/rachelnabors/pen/eJyWzm?editors=0010\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Follow the White Rabbit </a>, puedes asignar&nbsp; a <code>rabbitDownAnimation</code> un&nbsp; <code>id</code> de esta manera:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>rabbitDownAnimation<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>effect<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>id <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"rabbitGo\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificaciones","title":"Especificaciones","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/web-animations-1/#dom-animation-id\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Web Animations<br><small lang=\"es\">La definición de 'Animation.id' en esta especificación.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">Working Draft</span></td>\n   <td>Editor's draft.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Compatibilidad del navegador","id":"compatibilidad_del_navegador","isH3":false,"query":"api.Animation.id","dataURL":"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/id/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ver_también","title":"V